<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-20896] Accord: Topology compaction omits image records if minEpoch is ahead of last image</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20896</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;    Topology compaction omits image records if minEpoch is ahead of last image&lt;br/&gt;
    Also Fix:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;RegisteredCallback should remove itself from callback map when cancelled&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Do not throw CancellationException when processing requests that have been aborted, as may be caused by a successful meaningful reply that can be overridden&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;system_accord_debug.
{executors,coordinations}
&lt;p&gt; fail with ClassCastException&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;CommandStore.updateMinHlc eats up CPU as called much too often&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AccordCache not notifying flushed on shutdown&lt;br/&gt;
    Also Improve:&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Improve violation information&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Support skipping Deps&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Violation information reported&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Sort CommandStore shards by id&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
